same day Ford
announced plans of its own to
invest in a

07:23.543 --> 07:25.378 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
plant in the U.S.

07:25.412 --> 07:32.085 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
