08:19.499 --> 08:22.635 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We will take a closer look at
all of this
later in the program.

08:22.669 --> 08:24.738 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Meanwhile, the
president-elect
tapped

08:24.771 --> 08:29.042 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
