for U.S.
trade representative.

08:29.075 --> 08:33.680 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Lighthizer served as a deputy in
that office
during the Reagan administration
and has called

08:33.713 --> 08:37.016 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
