president-elect said Lighthizer
will fight for -- quote -- "good
trade deals

08:42.088 --> 08:44.023 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
that put the American worker
first."

08:44.057 --> 08:47.994 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
