21:28.154 --> 21:29.989 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
And that's what we do.

21:30.022 --> 21:33.192 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
We try to make sure they
understand what types
of attacks we could be seeing in
